{
  "texts": [
    "We conduct training SAM using a batch size of 20 with 4 A100 GPUs.Datasets.",
    "We conduct zero-shot evaluations on Group Captioning and Storytelling tasks to evaluate SAM's generalization ability.",
    "Both tasks demand semantic alignment across contextually different images.",
    "For the group captioning task, we select three datasets: Conceptual [25], Animal and Vehicle [13].",
    "For the storytelling task, we select AESOP [40], VIST [15] and DM800K [6] as test sets.Metrics."
  ]
}